title: Honeyball hands exciting recruit Cheltenham entry
text: Honeyball hands exciting recruit Cheltenham entry Monday, 19 October 2015 (1 minute ago) ONE Cheltenham bumper holds the warmest of memories for trainer Anthony Honeyball and he may return to familiar surroundings on Saturday with a horse who "ran like the hounds of hell were on his tail" when winning his debut in June.
